  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/18/dropbox-for-android-now-lets-you-share-folders-with-friends/\"><img alt=\"Shared folders in Dropbox for Android\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/8a97afde671c90f969e1cfa4a37ad423/dropbox-android-shared-folders.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\nAndroid 版 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/dropbox\">Dropbox</a> 今天迎来了更新，其中最重大的改变，是加入了与他人分享文件夹、管理相关权限的功能。这样一来，用户就算在身边没有电脑的情况下也可以快速与好友共享信息了。其它方面的改进不算太多，不过现在通过 Google Play 就可以订阅 Dropbox Pro 了。除此之外，开发团队也表示在 2014 年初的时候会为 iOS 版新增同样的分享功能，所以 iDevice 用户就再稍等一下吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/12/17/dropbox-for-android-now-lets-you-share-folders-with-friends/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"https://blog.dropbox.com/2013/12/mobile-sharing-in-a-snap/\" target=\"_blank\">Dropbox Blog</a>、<a href=\"http://www.androidpolice.com/2013/12/17/dropbox-v2-3-12-adds-ability-to-invite-contacts-to-shared-folders-manage-sharing-settings-go-pro-via-in-app-purchase-and-more/\" target=\"_blank\">Android Police</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dropbox.android\" target=\"_blank\">Google Play</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/18/dropbox-for-android-now-lets-you-share-folders-with-friends/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20791037/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/18/dropbox-for-android-now-lets-you-share-folders-with-friends/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
